lead_paragraph: Belarus manager Alexander Khatskevich has quit after refusing to take a pay cut following poor results in World Cup qualifying, the Belarus Football Federation (BFF) said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Belarus Manager Resigns After Refusing to Take Pay Cut
